# Connect Auditor working folder (per-surface checkpoints + staged patches).
# Local-only by design: each dev's audit run is independent and resumable
# without polluting git history. The auditor and apply prompts live in
# .github/ and .github/prompts/ — see .github/agents/connect-auditor.agent.md
.audit/

# Temporary Codex session offloads and extracted design references.
.Codex/sessions/

.vitest-p2.log
.vitest*.log

vitest-out.txt

v.txt
vitest-out.txt

# Capacitor webDir (generated by npm run build:mobile)
/mobile-dist/
